#: src/pages/Status.tsx
#~ msgid "Blocks Ocean found in the last 7d, with the same network-share luck multiplier. 7d smooths the short-term Poisson variance: a sustained <0.7× over a week suggests something structural (lower hashrate share than the estimator implies, or a real upstream issue at Ocean)."
